        "heading_6ULV8b": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "ANIMAL CHARITIES",
            "heading_tag": "h1"
          }
        },
        "richtext_jtmcxj": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>We love animals & want to help spread the word of the amazing people and organizations who are doing incredible things preserving the many beautiful animal species on our planet! The startling reality is that over 35-150 species become extinct every day due to inconsiderate human practices such as deforestation, mass culling for commercial activities and poaching for recreational purposes.<br/><br/>We would hate to see a world where animals become extinct due to human interference or a world with only captive animals, and at the rate we are going this is a very scary reality. So we are doing our small bit to help out! If you are interested in finding out more on any of these charities please visit the links below.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "image_NTjPmD": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Carbon_Neutral_Logo_480x480_5b11d303-293b-47bc-b38c-2bbad35decf7.png",
            "width_mode": "custom",
            "max_width": 300,
            "mobile_max_width": 200
          }
        },
        "richtext_LQKqt4": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Beserk, like any business, depends on the environment in many ways. We are proudly an environmentally friendly business that uses resources efficiently to reduce our carbon impact as much as possible. We partner with Carbon Neutral to help fund the planting of biodiverse native trees in degraded areas of Western Australia, helping to restore habitat to threatened flora and fauna.<br/><br/>If you have any suggestions for animal charities that need support we would love to hear from you!<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        }
      },
