            "title": "Coral Gardeners",
            "heading_tag": "h3",
            "content": "<p>Coral Gardeners work to save coral reefs globally through active reef restoration, awareness activities and innovative solutions.<br/><br/><a href=\"https://coralgardeners.org/\" target=\"_blank\">&gt;WEBSITE&lt;</a><br/><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/coralgardeners/\" target=\"_blank\">&gt;FACEBOOK&lt;</a></p>",
